{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "迎击战～万圣节·僵尸来袭～ 不死危机",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "梅露莎和阿加莎在湖边找到了这次骚动的\\n幕后黑手——帝国魔法师。她们向魔法师\\n发起奇袭，试图夺下魔导书。然而，\\n阿加莎却遭到埋伏好的僵尸队长偷袭，\\n并因魔导书之力而变为了僵尸。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "为从操纵僵尸的人手上\\n夺下魔导书，梅露莎\\n与阿加莎赶往湖畔。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "哎呀，梅露莎大人。你还在惦记留下来\\n当诱饵的那些人吗？还是说你在担心\\n留在圣城的希里丝大人他们的安危？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "都有……不过，我很在意\\n在城门遇到的那只僵尸说的话。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "“人质”……“为了家人”……\\n那些话到底是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我想应该是它们生前所抱有的\\n强烈情感脱口而出了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "在300年前的战争当中，\\n帝国在其统治的土地上\\n征用民兵，让他们投身战场。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "据我推测，当时帝国是以它的家人\\n为人质，强迫它参加战争吧。\\n所以它也只是个无辜百姓罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "听说被帝国抓起来的那些人在战后\\n都被释放，成了阿尔贝里亚王国的国民，\\n过上了安宁的生活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "但僵尸们并不知道这一事实，\\n至今仍在被迫战斗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "哎呀，你又眉头紧锁，\\n真是心地善良呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "那我给你出一道谜语吧。\\n不管是打仗还是打桩，什么东西\\n要是过度的话便会致命？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "打仗和打桩？是什么呢……\\n打桩……牢固……啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "阿加莎，\\n我懂你的意思了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "不过，不用担心。\\n为了解救希里丝他们，\\n现在可不能畏首畏尾。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "呵呵♪\\n看来是我杞人忧天了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "好了，差不多快到湖畔了。\\n抖擞精神，准备战斗吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "嗯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "喂，你按摩再轻一点啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "僵尸",
            "context": "啊呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "唉～那些僵尸，\\n还没攻下圣城吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "下命令倒是轻松，\\n但在这里干等就不见得了～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（那个魔法师手上拿的，\\n就是《不死军之书》。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "（只要夺下魔导书，\\n应该就能停止僵尸们的攻击。\\n可是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "（四周有一大堆僵尸……\\n怕是很难接近他。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（梅露莎大人，现在\\n该使用那个东西了吧？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "（啊，说得也是。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "我都说了！\\n给我轻轻地按摩啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "僵尸",
            "context": "啊呜……啊？啊呜啊呜！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "喂，手别停啊！咦？\\n有什么东西飞过来了。\\n那是……火球？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "咳咳咳……该死！\\n僵尸们都被炸飞了！\\n到底是怎么回事！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "这是圣城里名为铳的武器。\\n罗卡族铁匠帮我们修理了一下之后，\\n这坏掉的武器也能使用一次了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "圣城……该死！\\n没想到你们能来到这里！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "已经没有僵尸保护你了。\\n乖乖把魔导书交出来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "我在古墓又是踩到陷阱，\\n又是遭到魔兽袭击，好不容易\\n才拿到这本魔导书！怎么可能交出去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "我要靠这群僵尸往上爬！\\n攻陷圣城，扬名立万，\\n最终登上皇帝的宝座！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "真是典型的小人物思想呢。\\n你怕是配不上那本魔导书吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "乖，听话。\\n不然……呵呵呵♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "喂！你想干什么！？\\n你别过来！别过来，别过来啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "才怪。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "僵尸从地面冒出来了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "王牌就得留到最后关头才用！\\n这家伙生前可是当队长的，\\n比其它僵尸强了不止一点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "快，动手吧！僵尸队长！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120203_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "僵尸队长",
            "context": "嗷啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "离阿加莎远点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "阿加莎，振作一点！\\n不会吧！？没有呼吸了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "哈哈哈！这就死了啊！\\n那就吃我这一招。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "“汝，将化身宿命之恶魔。\\n汝，须冲破仇恨之桎梏。\\n地狱之门，敞开吧”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "啊……呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "啊……啊啊啊啊！\\n呜呜呜呜呜呜！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "阿加莎！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "《不死军之书》真正的恐怖之处，\\n就在于能将杀死的敌人\\n变为自己的棋子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "好了，现在就只剩你了。\\n噢，可别想着逃跑哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "是刚才打倒的僵尸们……\\n已经复活了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "虽然我可以直接把你杀掉变成僵尸，\\n但毕竟我攻打圣城遇到了瓶颈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120077_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "所以，我就破例给你一次机会。\\n我留你一条命，但你得成为我的手下，\\n然后回圣城骗那些同伴落入我的陷阱。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我拒绝！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "秒拒？可是，你好好想想。\\n我可是使役着绝对不死的\\n最强无敌僵尸军团哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军魔法师",
            "context": "圣城连万分之一的胜算都没有。\\n既然如此，保全自己的性命\\n才是明智之举吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "无论如何\\n我都要救我的朋友。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "他们出于对我的信任，\\n才把我送出城。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "还有很多人\\n也为我而付出了努力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_04_0064",
